___________________________________________________Refrence_____________________________________________________

                                               : Refrence type :
Refrence Example 

	In Refrence types variable is declare to one variable as refrence no memory alocation is req  

   
Genral syntax:

datatype *var_name;
int *ptr; 




Example of Refrence types  

# include < bits.h > or <stdc.h> // any one can be use
using namespace

int main()
{
	int x = 100     //value if 100 store in x 
	
	//ref is arefrence to 100
	int& ref = x;
	
	//value of x changes to 200
	ref = 200;
	count << "ref =" << ref << end;
	
	//value of x changes to 500
	x = 500
	count << "ref =" << ref << end;
	
	return 0;
}
 output: 
 	x = 200
	ref = 500
